10
00:00:26.005 --> 00:00:29.008
We won't be going into any deep or complex data structures

11
00:00:29.008 --> 00:00:33.000
or programming constructs, but you will need to be able

12
00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:36.002
to hold your own from a development perspective.

13
00:00:36.002 --> 00:00:37.007
We will be building applications

14
00:00:37.007 --> 00:00:39.009
using the Spring Cloud projects,

15
00:00:39.009 --> 00:00:44.000
so our focus on Java will be quick and mostly ignored,

16
00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:46.005
so you will need to keep up on your own.

17
00:00:46.005 --> 00:00:47.004
For this course,

