25
00:01:07.004 --> 00:01:08.009
Finally, on the Java front,

26
00:01:08.009 --> 00:01:12.000
I ask that you have experience running Java applications

27
00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:15.005
either from the command line or via your IDE.

28
