00:01:29.003 --> 00:01:32.005
and execute the run commands for a Java application,

35
00:01:32.005 --> 00:01:35.004
package it as a JAR, you will be fine.

36
00:01:35.004 --> 00:01:38.005
This course is a Spring course,

37
00:01:38.005 --> 00:01:40.004
so there is an expectation of knowledge

