00:02:10.008 --> 00:02:14.002
to move through this course, but I will move rather fast

49
00:02:14.002 --> 00:02:16.005
through the basic Spring constructs.

50
00:02:16.005 --> 00:02:19.003
If you are not super comfortable with Spring,

51
00:02:19.003 --> 00:02:20.008
I would encourage you to run

