00:02:35.008 --> 00:02:38.002
for basic Spring constructs.

58
00:02:38.002 --> 00:02:40.007
Again, if you need a refresher,

59
00:02:40.007 --> 00:02:44.003
check out the other courses that I have on Spring.

60
00:02:44.003 --> 00:02:47.000
Some of the other Spring packages that we will look at

61
00:02:47.000 --> 00:02:50.007
in this course are Spring Data, Spring MVC,

